nodecaption: Lysosomes digest Junk, until they become filled with LF
Free Fe, released by digestion, or trapped in LF, reacts with H2O2 to make HO*

LF - filled Lysosoms have reduced capacity & reduced rate of digesting Junk. They demand more lytic enzymes from Golgi, so less enzymes go to functional Lysosomes. Apgy becomes inhibited when Lysms cannot accept more junk.
